@flippyrulz123 The game was too easy. Multi-bottle rockets, bags of Dragonite, and Ness's endgame power up are just a few examples.

I'm not one to nitpick about graphics, but even I have standards.  I mean, the art style's nice, but there is no animation here. Try watching Venus's show in Fourside. If you can stomach it, you have a much longer attention span than me, friend.

The combat is boring. Nothing keeps it interesting to me.  It just doesn't set itself apart in any meaningful way.
